{"type": "article", "id": 29454, "title": "Adidas又起诉别家抄袭了，以及，小贝儿子掌镜了Burberry香水广告｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-12T03:01:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 35, "name": "复古"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 620, "name": "韩国"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 5782, "name": "诉讼"}, {"id": 8140, "name": "抄袭"}, {"id": 15085, "name": "刀锋战士"}, {"id": 19764, "name": "街头品牌"}, {"id": 30070, "name": "滑板文化"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1686, "name": "Marc Jacobs"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 1922, "name": "Celine"}, {"id": 2744, "name": "IMG"}, {"id": 9725, "name": "Skechers"}, {"id": 30071, "name": "Critic"}, {"id": 1715, "name": "Christopher Bailey"}, {"id": 30072, "name": "Marco Gobbetti"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712104247Uiyn75hMabvu0LWO.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/marc-jacobs-partners-imgs-made-to-measure-10484182/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Marc Jacobs  与 IMG 公司合作</b></a>｜设计师 Marc Jacobs 将与 IMG 公司的 Made to Measure 团队合作，制作<i> Off Book</i> 第二季节目。这是一档模特阅读来自文学作品、影戏和音乐中一段文字内容的节目。全部 10 期节目内的 8 位模特穿着将由 Marc Jacobs 赞助。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/financial/tiffany-reed-krakoff-design-accessories-housewares-10484155/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tiffany 将与设计师 Reed Krakoff 合作</b></a>｜设计师 Reed Krakoff 将与珠宝品牌 Tiffany 合作发布 2017 礼品、家居及配饰系列，Tiffany 设计总监 Francesca Amfitheatrof 继续掌管珠宝部门，两者都将向 CEO Frederic Cumenal 报告。同时 Krakoff  还将与 Tiffany 的视觉营销、广告团队合作产品的陈列及市场活动。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/burberry-shakeup-christopher-bailey-out-marco-gobbetti-new-ceo-10485024/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Burberry CEO 换人</b></a>｜英国奢侈品牌 Burberry 宣布 CEO 职位变动，将由 Céline   的 CEO Marco Gobbetti 接替 Christopher Bailey 的位置，同时 Julie Brown 担任首席运营及首席财政官。早前 Burberry 已经对 Christopher Bailey 进行减薪 75% 的处理。Bailey 从 2014 年 5 月开始担任创意总监兼 CEO，将只保留创意总监职位。</p><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/adidas-sues-skechers-in-patent-lawsuit\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Adidas 起诉 Skechers抄袭</b></a>｜近日，Adidas 控告 Skechers 的 Mega Flex 系列抄袭其“刀锋战士”跑鞋设计。Adidas 于 2013 年首发的 “刀锋战士”技术（&nbsp;Springblade），曾在与 Rick Owens 的联名系列中使用。这也不是两大运动品牌第一次出现冲突，今年早些，Adidas 还在诉讼 Skechers 抄袭其 Stan Smith 的案子中获胜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712100035wKutk1Mv7pEB3qRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">纽约品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/dee-ricky-puma-new-york-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Dee &amp; Ricky 与 Puma 再度合作联名系列</a>，预计七月中旬发布：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712101644TtN7B9sfkyXraIW0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712101644qrsiJAPZaDwnEMON.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712101644mxFPGybpwaAdB3R4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712101645Zhi8g6AuIxTSvqHP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712101645Zo7qJlj6b35kEANC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712101645hwyZeXqNzWOnBrvt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712101646JOCBkbLuWhAajm5r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>韩国街头品牌